### HYMN XXI

#### A prayer to Indra for protection

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0102101">1</span></span>Lord of the
clans, giver of bliss, fiend-slayer, mighty o'er the  
   foe,  
  May Indra, Soma-drinker, go before us, Bull, who brings us  
   peace.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0102102">2</span></span>Indra,
subdue our enemies, lay low the men who fight with  
   us:  
  Down into nether darkness send the man who shows us enmity:  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0102103">3</span></span>Strike down
the fiend, strike down the foes, break thou asunder  
  Vritra's jaws.  
  O Indra, Vritra-slayer, quell the wrath of the assailing foe.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0102104">4</span></span>Turn thou
the foeman's thought away, his dart who fain would  
   conquer us:  
  Grant us thy great protection; keep his deadly weapon far  
   away.  
  

